DOC.brief_summary: The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the safety and tolerability of ONO-6950 across ascending multiple doses in healthy adult male and female subjects. The secondary objectives are to characterize the PK and pharmacodynamic (PD) profiles of ONO-6950 by measuring plasma concentrations of ONO-6950 and pulmonary function.
DOC.brief_title: Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of ONO-6950 in Healthy Adult Subjects
DOC.criteria: Healthy nonsmoking male or female subjects (1855 inclusive) Body mass index (BMI)of 1035 kg/m2 (inclusive) For females; postmenopausal, nonlactating, and nonpregnant History or presence of clinical significant disease
